T1  - Invest Local or Remote? The Effects of COVID-19 Lockdowns on Venture Capital Investment Around the World
AU  - Han, Pengfei
AU  - Liu, Chunrui
AU  - Tian, Xuan
AU  - Wang, Kexin
Y1  - 2025/08/20
PY  - 2025
